"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"The Bitcoin hash rate is nearing an all-time high of [172 million terahashes](https://beincrypto.com/bitcoin-hash-rate-nears-all-time-high-as-mining-resettles/). That’s good considering that bitcoin [fell below $50,000](https://www.coindesk.com/markets/2021/12/09/bitcoin-drops-below-50k-support-between-43k-45k/) this week. The biggest fool in finance wants to [tell you why](https://www.fool.com/investing/2021/12/09/cathie-wood-bitcoin-price-target-updated-to-550000/). Despite the fall, Bloomberg Intelligence is calling for bitcoin to [hit $100,000](https://cointelegraph.com/news/bitcoin-could-hit-100k-gold-2k-in-2022-thanks-to-deflationary-forces-bloomberg-analyst). One analyst, however, says bitcoin could [fall another 20 percent](https://www.marketwatch.com/story/why-bitcoin-may-face-another-20-plunge-in-coming-weeks-as-risk-is-heightened-says-prominent-technical-analyst-were-watching-37-000-11639081370) in the next few weeks. Billy Bambrough is optimistic. He says the [U.S could adopt bitcoin](https://www.forbes.com/sites/billybambrough/2021/12/09/us-could-embrace-crypto-in-2022-huge-bitcoin-and-ethereum-price-prediction-revealed/?sh=11c9b392672a) in 2022. What’s he know that I don’t?\\n\\nDespite such bullish sentiments on the granddaddy of crypto, professional traders are [more favorable](https://cointelegraph.com/news/data-shows-pro-traders-are-currently-more-bullish-on-ethereum-than-bitcoin) toward Ethereum. Yet, Ethereum gas fees are through the roof, which [benefits smaller blockchains](https://markets.businessinsider.com/news/currencies/ethereum-transaction-gas-fees-high-solana-avalanche-cardano-crypto-blockchain-2021-12) like Solana and Avalanche. Also, one Ethereum transaction produces enough energy to [power a house](https://cointelegraph.com/news/ethereum-transaction-energy-use-equals-to-2-5-miles-in-a-tesla-model-3-report) all day. Still, one prominent Ethereum developer would rather talk about [NFTs and the metaverse](https://news.yahoo.com/ethereum-developer-sounds-off-on-nf-ts-metaverse-and-dystopian-facebook-153021379.html). See Dick jump through hoops?\\n\\nBinance is in talks with Indonesia’s wealthiest family regarding a new [crypto trading exchange](https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-12-10/binance-weighs-crypto-venture-with-indonesia-s-richest-family). In Australia, Binance is the first crypto exchange to begin [ESG reporting](https://coingape.com/breaking-binance-australia-becomes-first-ever-crypto-exchange-to-start-esg-reportage/).\\n\\nMeta’s new wallet Novi has launched allowing users to [send crypto](https://markets.businessinsider.com/news/currencies/meta-novi-crypto-wallet-pilot-program-whatsapp-facebook-cryptocurrency-2021-12) through WhatsApp.\\n\\nBitMart was hacked and the ne’er-do-wells behind it got away with [$200 million worth of Shiba Inu](https://u.today/200-million-worth-shiba-inu-and-other-tokens-stolen-from-bitmart-exchange) (and other tokens). There’s no use crying over spilled SHIB. Meanwhile, Google search data reveals that searches for “delete BitMart” rose 317 percent in one day. Data reported by [Case Monkey](https://www.casemonkey.co.uk/).\\n\\nPolygon is investing up to [250 MATIC](https://cointelegraph.com/news/polygon-to-invest-up-to-250m-matic-into-zero-knowledge-tech) into zero-knowledge technology. On another front, the rising blockchain star is buying Mir, an Ethereum scaling startup, [for $400 million](https://www.coindesk.com/business/2021/12/09/polygon-acquires-ethereum-scaling-startup-mir-for-400m-in-matic/).\\n\\nBudweiser launched almost 2,000 NFT beer cans, but the marketplace got bogged down by traffic. I guess it was *suds hour* in St. Louis, Missouri. Of course, when it comes to NFTs, it matters how you invest. Want to know how to be a [successful NFT trader](https://ambcrypto.com/here-are-the-traits-of-a-successful-nft-trader/)? **Read the full report [here](https://go.chainalysis.com/rs/503-FAP-074/images/Chainalysis%20NFT%20Market%20Report.pdf).**\\n\\nIn India, [a new bill](https://www.digit.in/news/crypto/crypto-bill-could-propose-arrest-without-warrant-for-violation-of-new-laws-report-62167.html) could ban crypto as a form of payment. The bill stipulates that those who run afoul of the law would give authorities the power to arrest them without a warrant and hold them without bail.\\n\\nReserve Bank of Australia governor says support for central bank digital currencies and smartphone tokens could be on the way for retailers. BUT, he predicts [they’ll be centralized](https://www.channelnews.com.au/rba-supports-central-bank-digital-currency/).\\n\\n[UK politicians](https://cointelegraph.com/news/uk-politicians-say-cryptocurrency-is-not-an-investment) do not consider cryptocurrency an investment.\\n\\nDid cryptocurrency fuel [a revolution](https://www.splcenter.org/hatewatch/2021/12/09/how-cryptocurrency-revolutionized-white-supremacist-movement) for white supremacists?\\n\\nSelf-proclaimed bitcoin inventor Craig Wright ordered to pay $100 million to W&K Info Defense Research as court [clears him of fraud charges](https://blockchain.news/news/self-acclaimed-bitcoin-inventor-craig-wright-vindicated-in-kleiman-lawsuit).\\n\\nThe CIA is getting in on the [crypto game](https://markets.businessinsider.com/news/currencies/cia-cryptocurrency-projects-in-works-confirming-rumors-director-says-2021-12).\\n\\nTron has built the first ever ecological complex in Cryptovoxels. Now, I have a metaverse complex.\\n\\nHong Kong real estate tycoon builds a [virtual land empire](https://www.forbes.com/sites/zinnialee/2021/12/08/hong-kong-property-tycoon-adrian-cheng-builds-virtual-land-in-the-sandboxs-metaverse/?sh=327302b645d8) in The Sandbox’s metaverse.\\n\\nSpeaking of metaverses, Uphold is hosting [a live webinar](https://event.webinarjam.com/register/112/n6879h8o) about the metaverse. And here’s a list of [metaverse tokens](https://markets.businessinsider.com/news/currencies/best-performing-cryptocurrencies-metaverse-tokens-of-the-year-2021-12) to keep an eye on.\\n\\nKickstarter is trying to stay relevant by migrating toward blockchain technology and users are [kicking bald tires mad](https://futurism.com/kickstarter-creators-furious-blockchain) over it.\\n\\nCongress’s Financial Service Committee held a hearing on stablecoins and [left Tether out](https://tokenist.com/tether-didnt-even-show-up-to-cryptos-biggest-regulatory-hearing-yet/). And *Foreign Policy* says the legislative body should [regulate cryptocurrencies](https://foreignpolicy.com/2021/12/07/cryptocurrency-regulation-congress-hearing-stablecoin-digital-currency/) now.\\n\\nCNBC says [investors of all ages](https://www.cnbc.com/2021/12/09/you-should-have-crypto-in-your-portfolio-no-matter-your-age.html) should have crypto in their portfolios. I couldn’t agree more. The latest report says [one-third of professional investors](https://www.p2pfinancenews.co.uk/2021/12/09/third-of-professional-investors-have-recently-invested-in-crypto/) have recently invested in crypto. Looks like we’re a ways off.\\n\\n*For informational and educational purposes only. Not financial advice. First published in [Cryptocracy](https://cryptocracy.substack.com/p/bitcoin-hash-rate-vs-ethereum-gas).*\\n\\n**Image credit:** Chainalysis\",\"timestamp\":1639222941,\"title\":\"Crypto traders prefer ETH to BTC\"},\"digest\":\"sGWRRjxUwwD_Yi8exdQHNQjoDdpq-W_br23zfSOe2uU\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xF3ADd46D4b718Fc2a87FcE85c18b6eD00c088b23\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ttaUXxocGcK4pI8TBtBFXWtd5zaiE_47dvIjJjYlW0U\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"ZAJohCcCySSN4x9tNViCRlVilvKzDa6hVg9MkFvtKRQ\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"gzTx29SgCo7EdsQN1cF9I56u98raf59yG4ZXBUYY8MHplTkZyjL9y9-lyB_GJi43KicDQG92A8op8hx8zVlvVQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xb163b8ef4553fdfd3eae56d1afecd3983646aa15f1b319ce5a5f590704ec8e8568174aaf010a7cf661c5ad9d1249d5aaf7efc7a8c574df3ea7945dbf893adad41c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ttaUXxocGcK4pI8TBtBFXWtd5zaiE_47dvIjJjYlW0U\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"ZAJohCcCySSN4x9tNViCRlVilvKzDa6hVg9MkFvtKRQ\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"JYRtRjslAR1HF1Pit-C-jiHwvtDz2_pfDR43NXQbJN0\"}"